http://support.amd.com/US/GPUDOWNLOAD/WINDOWS/Pages/downloads.aspx

Just pick out your OS in the left column and download the Catalyst Software Suite. This installs a driver that is designed to work with all video cards of the Radeon X series. What it does is actually downgrading the driver to a version that is less optimized for your specific video card, but it seems to work perfectly for all my games.

